reviewText: At least the young women show some modeling experience.  There is not a lot on the DVD, and of the 13 short film features, several are interviews with the model, and there are two studio shoots.  It is not a compelling DVD to buy.  As in past DVD by David, he uses flash outdoors, which is distracting, and get into the shot too often.  And likes to photograph far away.  If the intent is to drive traffic to his site, I think it fails based on what he shows.

Like the previous reviews I was completely disappointed with this DVD. Everything said before is correct.  Don't waste a cent on this DVD.  I will be tossing it out very soon as a waste of space in my collection.

I purchased this movie as part of a "package deal". I sent it back to Amazon and received about half the purchase price back.  I consider myself lucky!  This is a very poorly made movie that has no value or purpose.  Basically, buyers are paying for the producer's trip to other countries.  These are not the models that one would expect based on the title  I'm certain that they must be nice people, but I wouldn't consider them to be models.  Buy a Play Boy dvd instead.  You'll be much more satisfied.  If you are an ammature photographer seeking professional tips on how to take better photos, you won't get them from this dvd.

I've been to Ukraine and it's hard to find a fat woman under 35, yet this video showcases a chubby woman, exact opposite of what you think of regarding Ukrainian women.
